sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant FastAPI
    participant Neo4j
    participant Celery
    
    Client->>FastAPI: POST /graph/upsert (extraction_data)
    FastAPI->>Celery: Queue graph upsert task
    Celery->>Neo4j: Create/update nodes & relationships
    Note over Neo4j: Label separation:<br/>:CVE/:CWE (knowledge)<br/>:DiscoveredVulnerability (findings)
    Celery->>FastAPI: Task completion callback
    
    Client->>FastAPI: POST /graph/hybrid-search (query)
    FastAPI->>Neo4j: Vector + Graph search
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Fusion reranking
    FastAPI->>Client: Return ranked results